In Europe, the emphasis on sustainable practices is evident. The market is projected to grow at a CAGR of 4% as countries like Germany and France implement eco-friendly manufacturing technologies. The European Union's regulations on emissions are pushing manufacturers to adopt energy-efficient solutions, thus driving sales of advanced trolley resistance furnaces.

